{"tha-ap497:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap497:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap497:0.3":"Upaddhadussadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap497:1.1":"“Padumuttarabhagavato, ","tha-ap497:1.2":"sujato nama savako; ","tha-ap497:1.3":"Pamsukulam gavesanto, ","tha-ap497:1.4":"sankare carate tada. ","tha-ap497:2.1":"Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap497:2.2":"paresam bhatako aham; ","tha-ap497:2.3":"Upaddhadussam datvana, ","tha-ap497:2.4":"sirasa abhivadayim. ","tha-ap497:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap497:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap497:3.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap497:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap497:4.1":"Tettimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap497:4.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap497:4.3":"Sattasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap497:4.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap497:5.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap497:5.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap497:5.3":"Upaddhadussadanena, ","tha-ap497:5.4":"modami akutobhayo. ","tha-ap497:6.1":"Icchamano caham ajja, ","tha-ap497:6.2":"sakananam sapabbatam; ","tha-ap497:6.3":"Khomadussehi chadeyyam, ","tha-ap497:6.4":"addhadussassidam phalam. ","tha-ap497:7.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap497:7.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap497:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap497:7.4":"addhadussassidam phalam. ","tha-ap497:8.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap497:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap497:8.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap497:9.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap497:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap497:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap497:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap497:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap497:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap497:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upaddhadussadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap497:12.1":"Upaddhadussadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}